  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a large bowl, mix flour and chocolate chips. Add melted butter, salt, and passata.",
    "Stir in sugar and lemon juice until combined. Spread into an ungreased baking dish.",
    "Whisk together zest, remaining sugar, and lemon juice for the crumble topping.",
    "Sprinkle over the top of the tart. Bake 25-30 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Cool before serving."
